<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM9.5">
<l>tuṅka malarppoḻil cūḻtiru māliruñ cōlainiṉṟa</l>
<l>ceṅkaṭ karumuki liṉti ruvurup pōlmalarmēl</l>
<l>toṅkiya vaṇṭiṉaṅ kāḷtoku pūñcuṉai kāḷcuṉaiyil</l>
<l>taṅkucen tāmarai kāḷeṉak kōrcaraṇ cāṟṟumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O swarms of bees that abide on to the flowers like the lustrous form of</l>
<l rend="indent">the red-eyed dark Cloud</l>
<l>who has stood in Tirumāliruñcōlai, surrounded by tall groves with flowers!</l>
<l>O beautiful ponds that crowd together!</l>
<l>O red lotuses that abide in [those] ponds! Do mention a refuge for me!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
